      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously maintained to the highest standard. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine, and the interior remains in pristine condition, looking and smelling like new. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with a smooth engine, precise transmission, and a complete service history that confirms its exceptional care. Buyers can expect a vehicle that drives as well as it did the day it left the factory, offering a rare opportunity to own a top-tier example of this model.",
