      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into luxury with this absolutely pristine, showroom-quality vehicle! It is in mint condition and looks as if it just rolled off the assembly line, offering a flawless driving experience and an immaculate interior. This is a rare find for a buyer who truly appreciates a car that has been cared for with the utmost perfection!",
