    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is ideal for a buyer looking for a reliable daily driver without the premium price of a newer model. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a few small dings on the passenger side panels, and some fading on the trim. Inside, the upholstery shows visible wear and some minor staining, though the cabin remains functional and smoke-free. Mechanically, the car starts and runs well, though it lacks the smoothness of a newer vehicle and may require some routine maintenance soon. It is a solid, honest car that has served its previous owner well and still has plenty of life left for its next journey.",
      "price": 22500.0,
