    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride that's ready for all your weekend adventures? This car has been so good to me and is still in solid, dependable shape for its next owner. It drives smoothly and has been well-loved, making it the perfect choice if you want quality without the brand-new price tag. I'm looking for a quick, easy sale, so come take it for a spin and see why I've enjoyed it so much!",
      "price": 28500.0,
