      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio to achieve its 8,400 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a lightning-quick 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque vectoring across the rear axle. The chassis remains structurally sound with the factory-spec aluminum multi-link suspension and M-tuned kinematics providing precise turn-in. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators to address common platform vulnerabilities. While the Interlagos Blue finish shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical synchronization and vanos timing remain within tight tolerances, offering a visceral, analog driving experience.",
      "price": 31850.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
