    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily utility. The exterior retains its deep, high-gloss luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with highway commuting. The body panels are straight with no major dings or previous accident history. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment featuring supple leather seating with only light bolster wear on the driver\u2019s side. All electronic components\u2014including the premium sound system, dual-zone climate control, and navigation\u2014are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is robust; it has a complete service log, with a recent oil service and brake inspection performed just last month. The tires provide excellent grip with plenty of tread remaining. This is a reliable, turn-key example ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
